  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      364.96,
      384.07,
      378.24
    ],
    "text": "Six Killed in Fatal Road Accident \u2013 Meegoda Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      392.8,
      510.5,
      447.5
    ],
    "text": "A tragic road accident occurred on the night of 31 May 2026 within the jurisdiction of the Meegoda Police Division. A cab travelling towards Colombo from Avissawella along the High Level Road struck a group of people who were standing in a queue at a Dansala near the Meegoda Junction before fleeing the scene.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      462.06,
      510.31,
      502.94
    ],
    "text": "A total of 13 injured persons were admitted to the Homagama Hospital for treatment. Among them, three men and three women succumbed to their injuries while receiving medical attention.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      517.38,
      518.93,
      558.26
    ],
    "text": "Police officers deployed at the Godagama Junction responded promptly to the incident and successfully apprehended the cab involved, along with its driver, who had attempted to escape.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      572.85,
      497.97,
      599.93
    ],
    "text": "The deceased comprise residents of the Hanwella, Avissawella, and Piliyandala areas, ranging in age from 15 to 56 years.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      614.37,
      520.65,
      655.25
    ],
    "text": "The suspect driver, a 42-year-old resident of Piliyandala, was taken into custody. Preliminary investigations have confirmed that he was under the influence of alcohol at the time of the accident.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      669.81,
      519.65,
      696.89
    ],
    "text": "Seven injured victims remain hospitalized at the Homagama Hospital and are continuing to receive treatment.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      711.45,
      398.59,
      724.73
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Meegoda Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
